# Integrations

## Rules

- Offline-first (no external APIs)
- Local file storage
- Type-safe integrations
- Test with Docker environment

## Anti-Patterns

**❌ External APIs:** Use mock implementations for offline-first
**❌ Cloud storage:** Store files locally, not in S3/Cloudinary/etc.
